view

Class StudentPane

  • java.lang.Object
    • view.StudentPane

  • public class StudentPane
extends java.lang.Object
    This class will build the View For a Student Pane where the user can build Student Object. Student info will then be sent to Ram. Where the controller will make a student object. Display button will pop up a new window that displays all Student in an ArrayList.
    Author:
    Caio
